casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Anthony Gestail TUCKER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 152798
COA: 322151 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 5, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion to withdraw the application for leave to appeal is considered, and it is GRANTED. We VACATE this Court's order of May 25, 2018, granting leave to appeal. Accordingly, the application for leave to appeal is DISMISSED.
